### Font Families

| Role | Family | Fallback |
|------|--------|----------|
| **Sans** (UI text) | `Inter` | `system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif` |
| **Mono** (code, labels) | `JetBrains Mono` | `ui-monospace, monospace` |
| **Serif** (editorial, optional) | — | — |

### Type Scale

| Name | Size | Line Height | Weight | Usage |
|------|------|-------------|--------|-------|
| `text-xs` | 12px | 16px | 400 | Labels, captions, metadata |
| `text-sm` | 14px | 20px | 400 | Body small, secondary text |
| `text-base` | 16px | 24px | 400 | Default body text |
| `text-lg` | 18px | 28px | 400–500 | Subtitles, emphasized body |
| `text-xl` | 20px | 28px | 500–600 | Section headings (small) |
| `text-2xl` | 24px | 32px | 600 | Page section headings |
| `text-3xl` | 30px | 36px | 700 | Page titles |
| `text-4xl+` | 36px+ | 40px+ | 700–800 | Hero / landing headings |

### Weight Conventions

- **400** — Body, descriptions, secondary content
- **500** — Medium emphasis, navigation items
- **600** — Subheadings, button labels, emphasis
- **700** — Headings, strong emphasis
- **800+** — Hero text, large display only

