| `gap-1` / `p-1` | 4px | Tight element spacing |
| `gap-2` / `p-2` | 8px | Internal padding, small gaps |
| `gap-4` / `p-4` | 16px | Standard component padding |
| `gap-6` / `p-6` | 24px | Card padding, section gaps |
| `gap-8` / `p-8` | 32px | Large section spacing |
| `gap-12` / `gap-16` | 48–64px | Page section separators |

### Breakpoints

