| `sm` | 640px | Large mobile / small tablet |
| `md` | 768px | Tablet |
| `lg` | 1024px | Desktop |
| `xl` | 1280px | Wide desktop |
| `2xl` | 1536px | Ultra-wide (usually not needed) |

> **Mobile-first:** Default styles target mobile; use `md:` / `lg:` to scale up.

