## Interaction Design

<!-- TODO: fill in based on UI complexity and user preference -->

### Animation Philosophy

<!-- TODO: fill in — e.g. "Subtle and purposeful. No decorative animations." -->

### Transition Defaults

| Element | Duration | Easing |
|---------|----------|--------|
| Hover states | `150ms` | `ease-out` |
| Dropdowns / menus | `200ms` | `ease-out` |
| Modals / sheets | `250ms` | `ease-in-out` |
| Page transitions | `300ms` | `ease-in-out` |
| Skeleton → content | `400ms` | `ease-in` |

### Hover States

- Buttons: subtle background shift + `cursor-pointer`
- Links: underline on hover or color shift
- Cards (clickable): `shadow-md` on hover, slight `translate-y-[-1px]`
- Icons: `opacity-80` hover, full opacity active

### Loading Patterns

- **Skeleton loaders** — preferred for content areas (not spinners)
- **Button loading** — show spinner inside button, disable during action
- **Optimistic updates** — apply immediately, revert on error
- **Error states** — always provide a retry action

